Complete Product Requirement Document (PRD)
Product Name

STEM Quest

Tagline

Play. Learn. Explore. Build Your Future.

Problem Statement

Rural students from Classes 6–12 often experience:

Fear of Mathematics and Science
Lack of engaging learning methods
Limited access to quality STEM resources
Minimal exposure to practical experiments
Low confidence after repeated failures
Poor motivation due to rote learning

The platform addresses these challenges through curriculum-aligned gamification.

Vision

To make STEM education exciting, interactive, and confidence-building for every rural student.

Mission

Create India's most engaging gamified STEM platform that helps rural students:

Overcome fear
Develop scientific curiosity
Build confidence
Learn by doing
Improve academic performance
